  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 37,
      "chapterTitle": "小引",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "35990194_37_1666-1780",
          "range": "1666-1780",
          "rangeStart": 1666,
          "rangeEnd": 1780,
          "markText": "我有一时，曾经屡次忆起儿时在故乡所吃的蔬果：菱角，罗汉豆，茭白，香瓜。凡这些，都是极其鲜美可口的；都曾是使我思乡的蛊惑。后来，我在久别之后尝到了，也不过如此；惟独在记忆上，还有旧来的意味留存。他们也许要哄骗我一生，使我时时反顾。",
          "colorStyle": 2,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1746963903,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-05-11 19:45:03",
          "chapterUid": 37,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35990194&chapterUid=37&rangeStart=1666&rangeEnd=1780",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e7332a1072252ab2e732536?chapterUid=37&rangeStart=1666&rangeEnd=1780"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "35990194_37_467-545",
          "range": "467-545",
          "rangeStart": 467,
          "rangeEnd": 545,
          "markText": "我常想在纷扰中寻出一点闲静来，然而委实不容易。目前是这么离奇，心里是这么芜杂。一个人做到只剩了回忆的时候，生涯大概总要算是无聊了罢，但有时竟会连回忆也没有。",
          "colorStyle": 2,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1746963893,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-05-11 19:44:53",
          "chapterUid": 37,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35990194&chapterUid=37&rangeStart=467&rangeEnd=545",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e7332a1072252ab2e732536?chapterUid=37&rangeStart=467&rangeEnd=545"
        }
      ]
    }
